(1993, 1, '2022-10-01 21:48:14', '2022-10-01 21:48:14', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>A Light in the Attic&nbsp;</em>delights with remarkable characters and hilariously profound poems in a collection readers will return to again and again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here in the attic you will find Backward Bill, Sour Face Ann, the Meehoo with an Exactlywatt, and the Polar Bear in the Frigidaire. You will talk with Broiled Face, and find out what happens when Somebody steals your knees, you get caught by the Quick-Digesting Gink, a Mountain snores, and They Put a Brassiere on the Camel.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Come on up to the attic of Shel Silverstein and let the light bring you home.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1956,\"width\":407,\"height\":407,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a-light-in-the-attic-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"A light in the attic book\" class=\"wp-image-1956\" width=\"407\" height=\"407\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'A Light in the Attic', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a-light-in-the-attic', '', '', '2022-10-02 00:13:04', '2022-10-02 00:13:04', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1993', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(1995, 1, '2022-10-01 22:01:15', '2022-10-01 22:01:15', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Have you ever read a book with everything on it? Well, here it is! You will say Hi-ho for the toilet troll, get tongue-tied with Stick-a-Tongue-Out-Sid, play a highly unusual horn, and experience the joys of growing down.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What\'s that? You have a case of the Lovetobutcants? Impossible! Just come on in and let the magic of Shel Silverstein bend your brain and open your heart.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1965,\"width\":282,\"height\":362,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/everything-on-it.jpg\" alt=\"Every thing on it book\" class=\"wp-image-1965\" width=\"282\" height=\"362\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Every Thing On It', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'every-thing-on-it', '', '', '2022-10-02 00:13:30', '2022-10-02 00:13:30', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1995', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(1996, 1, '2022-10-01 22:07:06', '2022-10-01 22:07:06', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:shortcode -->\n<i>Once there was a tree... and she loved a little boy.</i>\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So begins a story of unforgettable perception, beautifully written and illustrated by the gifted and versatile Shel Silverstein. This moving parable for all ages offers a touching interpretation of the gift of giving and a serene acceptance of another\'s capacity to love in return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every day the boy would come to the tree to eat her apples, swing from her branches, or slide down her trunk...and the tree was happy. But as the boy grew older he began to want more from the tree, and the tree gave and gave and gave. This is a tender story, touched with sadness, aglow with consolation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>The Giving Tree</em>&nbsp;is a meaningful gift for milestone events such as graduations, birthdays, and baby showers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1979,\"width\":390,\"height\":523,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/the-giving-tree.jpg\" alt=\"The giving tree book\" class=\"wp-image-1979\" width=\"390\" height=\"523\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'The Giving Tree', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-giving-tree', '', '', '2022-10-02 00:13:43', '2022-10-02 00:13:43', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1996', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(1997, 1, '2022-10-02 03:04:04', '2022-10-02 03:04:04', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Runny Babbit</em>&nbsp;is Shel Silverstein\'s hilarious and&nbsp;<em>New York Times-</em>bestselling book of spoonerisms—words or phrases with letters or syllables swapped: bunny rabbit becomes Runny Babbit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to the world of Runny Babbit and his friends Toe Jurtle, Skertie Gunk, Rirty Dat, Dungry Hog, Snerry Jake, and many others who speak a topsy-turvy language all their own.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>So if you say, \"Let\'s bead a rook<br>That\'s billy as can se,\"<br>You\'re talkin\' Runny Babbit talk,<br>Just like mim and he.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And don\'t miss&nbsp;<em>Runny Babbit Returns</em>, the new book from Shel Silverstein!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1967,\"width\":402,\"height\":359,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/runny-babbit.jpg\" alt=\"runny babbit book\" class=\"wp-image-1967\" width=\"402\" height=\"359\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Runny Babbit', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'runny-babbit', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:14', '2022-10-05 05:20:14', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1997', 0, 'book', '', 0);
