(1998, 1, '2022-10-02 03:07:38', '2022-10-02 03:07:38', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Runny Babbit Returns</em>, a collection of 41 never-before-published poems and drawings, features Runny and other woodland characters who speak a topsy-turvy language all their own.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This carefully compiled work from the Silverstein archives is filled with spoonerism poems that are both playful and poignant. With tongue-twisting word play and uproarious characters, the endearingly befuddled Runny Babbit and his friends embody Shel Silverstein’s singular style, the one we all know and love.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fans of all ages won’t want to miss their chance to follow their favorite Runny in this&nbsp;<em>New York Times</em>&nbsp;bestseller of laugh-out-loud adventures!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1968,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/runny-babbit-returns.jpg\" alt=\"Runny babbit returns\" class=\"wp-image-1968\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Runny Babbit Returns', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'runny-babbit-returns', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:20', '2022-10-05 05:20:20', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1998', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(1999, 1, '2022-10-02 03:10:33', '2022-10-02 03:10:33', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>It was missing a piece. And it was not happy.&nbsp;</em>What it finds on its search for the missing piece is simply and touchingly told. This inventive and heartwarming book can be read on many levels, and Silverstein’s iconic drawings and humor are sure to delight fans of all ages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>So it set off in search<br>of its missing piece.<br>And as it rolled<br>it sang this song—<br>Oh I\'m lookin\' for my missin\' piece<br>I\'m lookin\' for my missin\' piece<br>Hi-dee-ho, here I go,<br>Lookin\' for my missin\' piece.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1975,\"width\":351,\"height\":428,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/the-missing-piece.jpg\" alt=\"The missing piece book\" class=\"wp-image-1975\" width=\"351\" height=\"428\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'The Missing Piece', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-missing-piece', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:27', '2022-10-05 05:20:27', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=1999', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(2001, 1, '2022-10-02 03:15:32', '2022-10-02 03:15:32', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This companion tale to The Missing Piece is an inventive and heartwarming book where the missing piece is in search of its perfect match. The missing piece sat alone...waiting for someone to come along and take it somewhere. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All it wants is to roll along with its perfect match, but some are too small, others too big, and some fit yet don\'t roll. The missing piece feels sad and lonely until it meets the Big O, and learns that all it ever needed was a little encouragement and determination to fulfill its dreams.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1976,\"width\":269,\"height\":317,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/the-missing-piece-meets-the-big-o.jpg\" alt=\"The missing piece meets the big o book\" class=\"wp-image-1976\" width=\"269\" height=\"317\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'The Missing Piece Meets the Big O', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-missing-piece-meets-the-big-o', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:33', '2022-10-05 05:20:33', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=2001', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(2002, 1, '2022-10-02 03:27:28', '2022-10-02 03:27:28', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"You don\'t have to shoot me,\" says the young lion. \"I will be your rug and I will lie in front of your fireplace and I won\'t move a muscle and you can sit on me and toast all the marshmallows you want. I love marshmallows.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But the hunter will not listen to reason, so what is there for a young lion to do? After eating up the hunter, Lafcadio takes the gun home and practices and practices until he becomes the world\'s greatest sharp-shooter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now dressed in starched collars and fancy suits, and enjoying all the marshmallows he wants, Lafcadio is pampered and admired wherever he goes. But is a famous, successful, and admired lion a happy lion? Or is he a lion at all?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Told and drawn with wit and gusto, Shel Silverstein\'s modern fable speaks not only to children but to us all!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1981,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/lafcadio.jpg\" alt=\"lafcadio, the lion who shot back \" class=\"wp-image-1981\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Lafcadio, The Lion Who Shot Back', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lafcadio-the-lion-who-shot-back', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:06', '2022-10-05 05:20:06', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=2002', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(2004, 1, '2022-10-02 03:50:35', '2022-10-02 03:50:35', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Featuring rhythmic verse and iconic illustrations,&nbsp;<em>A Giraffe and a Half</em>&nbsp;will leave every reader, young and old, laughing until the very end. Beloved for over fifty years, this classic captures Silverstein’s signature humor and style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>If you had a giraffe and he stretched another half, you would have a giraffe and a half</em>. But what happens if you glue a rose to the tip of his nose? Or if you used a chair to comb his hair? Join this giraffe on a rollicking and ridiculous journey that will charm readers from beginning to end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1957,\"width\":283,\"height\":349,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a-giraffee-and-a-half.jpg\" alt=\"A giraffe and a half book\" class=\"wp-image-1957\" width=\"283\" height=\"349\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'A Giraffe and A Half', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a-giraffe-and-a-half', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:19:48', '2022-10-05 05:19:48', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=2004', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(2005, 1, '2022-10-02 03:56:33', '2022-10-02 03:56:33', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A rhino makes the best kind of friend in this 50th Anniversary Edition of a cherished classic from Shel Silverstein.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Looking for a new pet? Bored with cats, dogs, goldfish, gerbils, and hamsters? How about a cheap rhinoceros?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shel Silverstein’s loving look at the joys of rhino ownership may convince you to be the lucky person who takes home this very, very unusual pet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":2007,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/who-wants-a-cheap-rhinoceros-1024x884.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2007\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Who Wants a Cheap Rhinoceros?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'who-wants-a-cheap-rhinoceros', '', '', '2022-10-05 05:20:39', '2022-10-05 05:20:39', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=book&#038;p=2005', 0, 'book', '', 0),
