(2071, 1, '2022-10-05 00:56:15', '2022-10-05 00:56:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Another cute, quirky, clever book of poetry by Silverstein. He was a favorite as a kid, for the humor in each and every poem. Now, as an adult, what I appreciate most is his clever word play.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Quirky In All The Best Ways', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'falling-up-2', '', '', '2022-10-05 00:57:38', '2022-10-05 00:57:38', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=review&#038;p=2071', 0, 'review', '', 0),
(2073, 1, '2022-10-05 00:59:00', '2022-10-05 00:59:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I really enjoyed reading the book as a kid. When I was reminded of it as an adult, I grabbed it immediately. I love reading poetry. I read way more as a child.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', ' One of my favorite childhood poetry books', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'one-of-my-favorite-childhood-poetry-books', '', '', '2022-10-05 00:59:00', '2022-10-05 00:59:00', '', 0, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?post_type=review&#038;p=2073', 0, 'review', '', 0),
