(2108, 1, '2022-10-05 04:31:15', '2022-10-05 04:31:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sheldon Silverstein was born in Chicago on September 25, 1930. He was an American writer, poet, cartoonist, songwriter, and playwright.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During his childhood, Silverstein had a desire to write, and that\'s when he developed his writing style and skills. In the 1950\'s, he served in the U.S military in Korea and Japan, and that\'s when he got a job as a cartoonist for the <em>Pacific Stars and Stripes</em>. After his service, he sold hotdogs at Chicago parks and continued to write cartoons for newspapers and national magazines.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In 1963 he published his first book, <em>Lafcadio, the Lion Who Shot Back</em>. Although, it was never in his plans to write or draw for children, a friend convinced him to follow this path. In 1964, <em>The Giving Tree</em>, which would become his most successful book, was published. It was four years before Silverstein found someone who would publish <em>The Giving Tree.</em> Some publishers thought the book was too sad to publish. In an interview with <em>Chicago Tribune</em>, Shel said, \"Because life, you know, has pretty sad endings. You don\'t have to laugh it up even if most of my stuff is humorous.\" <a href=\"http://www.shelsilverstein.com/about-shel/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://www.shelsilverstein.com/about-shel/\">(ShelSilverstein.com)</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"66.66%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In 1969, Silverstein released the song \"A Boy Named Sue\", which became a hit for Johnny Cash.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":2107,\"width\":360,\"height\":352,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/shel.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2107\" width=\"360\" height=\"352\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'About the Author', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-05 04:31:15', '2022-10-05 04:31:15', '', 2, 'https://fwolfeil.bitlampsites.com/wpd/new-final/?p=2108', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
